'''卡尔·达洛''' （{{lang-en|'''Karl Darlow'''}}，{{bd|1990年|10月8日|catIdx=F}}），[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[守門員_(足球)|守門員]]，效力於[[英超|英超]]球隊[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|纽卡斯尔联]]。

==球會生涯==
达洛16歲時便被[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]放棄，一星期後維拉守門員教練[[艾历·史迪尼|艾历·史迪尼]]向[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|诺丁汉森林]]推薦达洛，接著他便與森林青年軍簽約。在預備隊出色的表現，使他在2010/11球季提拔上一隊成為二號守門員，並在球季最後一場比賽首次參加職業聯賽，該場對[[水晶宫足球俱乐部|水晶宫]]比賽中替補身份換下[[李爾·甘普|李爾·甘普]]，森林以3-0獲勝並取得晉級附加賽資格<ref>{{cite news|title=Crystal Palace 0–3 Nott'm Forest|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/13247240|publisher=BBC|work=BBC Sport|date=7 May 2011|accessdate=13 March 2012|archive-date=2016-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160114142448/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/13247240|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2012年3月，达洛被外借至全國聯球會[[纽波特郡足球俱乐部|纽波特郡]]一個月<ref>{{cite news|title=Newport County sign young keeper Karl Darlow|date=8 March 2012|accessdate=13 March 2012|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/17306918|publisher=BBC|work=BBC Sport}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Potter Leaves|url=http://www.newport-county.co.uk/news/posts/page179.html|publisher=Newport County A.F.C.|work=newport-county.co.uk|date=8 March 2012|accessdate=13 March 2012|first=Chris|last=Blight|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120910001627/http://www.newport-county.co.uk/news/posts/page179.html|archivedate=2012年9月10日}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=New-Port of Call For Karl|url=http://www.nottinghamforest.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10308~2641925,00.html|date=9 March 2012|accessdate=13 March 2012|publisher=Nottingham Forest F.C.|work=nottinghamforest.co.uk|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120312132430/http://www.nottinghamforest.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10308~2641925,00.html|archivedate=2012年3月12日}}</ref>，首場比賽對[[盖茨黑德足球俱乐部|盖茨黑德]]並以1-0獲勝<ref>{{cite news|title=Newport County AFC V Gateshead|url=http://www.newport-county.co.uk/fixtures/yes/page21.html|date=31 March 2012|accessdate=16 April 2012|publisher=Newport County A.F.C.|work=newport-county.co.uk}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。2012年9月21日，他被外借到[[沃尔索尔足球俱乐部|沃尔索尔]]一個月<ref>{{cite news|title=Karl Heads Out|url=http://www.nottinghamforest.co.uk/news/article/karl-heads-out-380376.aspx|publisher=Nottingham Forest F.C.|work=nottinghamforest.co.uk|date=21 September 2012|accessdate=21 September 2012|first=Fraser|last=Nicholson|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303215850/http://www.nottinghamforest.co.uk/news/article/karl-heads-out-380376.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>，外借期間與母會森林簽下三年新約至2015年<ref>{{cite news|title=New Deal for Darlow|url=http://www.nottinghamforest.co.uk/news/article/new-deal-for-darlow-410567.aspx|publisher=Nottingham Forest F.C.|work=nottinghamforest.co.uk|date=5 October 2012|accessdate=5 October 2012|first=Nick|last=Richardson|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304053620/http://www.nottinghamforest.co.uk/news/article/new-deal-for-darlow-410567.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月22日，他的外借期延長至12月22日<ref>{{cite news|title=Karl's Staying With Walsall|url=http://www.nottinghamforest.co.uk/news/article/karls-staying-with-walsall-438733.aspx|date=22 October 2012|accessdate=25 October 2012|publisher=Nottingham Forest F.C.|work=nottinghamforest.co.uk|first=Fraser|last=Nicholson|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304060657/http://www.nottinghamforest.co.uk/news/article/karls-staying-with-walsall-438733.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。可是森林的替-{}-補守門員[[迪米特尔·叶夫季莫夫|迪米特尔·叶夫季莫夫]]受傷，他被提前召回<ref>{{cite news|title=Nottingham Forest recall Karl Darlow from Walsall|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20103173|work=BBC Sport|publisher=BBC|date=26 October 2012|accessdate=27 October 2012|archive-date=2012-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121030091513/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20103173|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年1月1日轉會窗開啟後，他被外借重返沃尔索尔至球季結束<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football-20882815|title=Walsall re-sign Nottingham Forest keeper on loan|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=1 January 2013|date=1 January 2013|archive-date=2013-04-20|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130420021857/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football-20882815|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但由於森林的一號門將李爾·甘普表示有意離隊，他在1月10日被召回解決森林門將問題的燃眉之急<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20933293|title=Nottingham Forest recall Karl Darlow from Walsall again|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=1 January 2013|date=10 January 2013|archive-date=2013-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130113022436/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20933293|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20973585|title=Lee Camp: Nottingham Forest will let goalkeeper leave|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=10 January 2013|date=10 January 2013|archive-date=2013-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130113015734/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/20973585|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1月12日以2-1擊敗[[彼得伯勒联足球俱乐部|彼得堡聯]]後，主教練[[亚历克斯·麥克萊什|亚历克斯·麥克萊什]]表示达洛會成為一號門將。
 
[[諾定咸森林2013年至2014年球季|2013/14球季]]，达洛獲分發1號球衣，成為了球隊的絕對主力。新球季中他首三場聯賽均保持不失球，對[[沃特福德足球俱乐部|沃特福德]]的賽事才被攻破大門，是英冠聯賽最後一位失球的守門員。

2014年8月9日，他與英超球會[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|纽卡斯尔联]]簽約加盟，並外借回諾定咸森林一個賽季<ref>{{cite web|last1=Marshall|first1=Anthony|title=United Complete Lascelles And Darlow Deal|url=http://www.nufc.co.uk/articles/20140809/united-complete-lascelles-and-darlow-deal_2281670_4055609|publisher=Newcastle United F.C.|accessdate=9 August 2014|date=9 August 2014|archive-date=2016-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161116051403/http://www.nufc.co.uk/articles/20140809/united-complete-lascelles-and-darlow-deal_2281670_4055609/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Magpies swoop for Jamaal and Karl|url=http://www.nottinghamforest.co.uk/news/article/magpies-swoop-for-jamaal-and-karl-1802814.aspx|publisher=Nottingham Forest F.C.|accessdate=9 August 2014|date=9 August 2014|archive-date=2016-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160324055217/http://www.nottinghamforest.co.uk/news/article/magpies-swoop-for-jamaal-and-karl-1802814.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==國家隊生涯== 
达洛的祖父[[肯·李克|肯·李克]]在{{link-en|因西比盧|Ynysybwl}}出生，因此他有資格代表[[威爾斯足球代表隊|威爾斯]]參賽，但[[威爾斯足球協會|威爾斯足球協會]]表示达洛拒絕了威爾斯的邀請參加2013年月6日的友誼賽<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.southwalesargus.co.uk/sport/football/newportcounty/10214301.Ex_County_stopper_Karl_Darlow_is_latest_to_say_no_to_a_Wales_call_up/ |title=Darlow declines Wales invitation |access-date=2014-06-07 |archive-date=2019-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190328120324/https://www.southwalesargus.co.uk/sport/football/newportcounty/10214301.Ex_County_stopper_Karl_Darlow_is_latest_to_say_no_to_a_Wales_call_up/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

